What's the purpose of this change? The old proof looks fine to me, and it's quite a bit cleaner.
I thought it'd make sense for this to be proved in terms of `Equiv.of_exists`. The proof is pretty much the same besides that.
I've golfed this theorem a bit, the correspondence between the old and new proof should now be much more obvious.

```suggestion
  induction o using Ordinal.induction with | h o IH =>
  let S := 긖 a 갣 Set.Iio o, {x : Game.{u} | birthday x < a}
  let H : Small.{u} S := @small_biUnion _ _ _ _ _ IH
  obtain rfl | 具빠, rfl具 | ho := zero_or_succ_or_limit o
  췅 simp_rw [Ordinal.not_lt_zero]
    exact small_empty
  췅 simp_rw [Order.lt_succ_iff, le_iff_lt_or_eq]
    convert small_union.{u} {x | birthday x < a} {x | birthday x = a}
    췅 exact IH _ (Order.lt_succ a)
    췅 let f (g g : Set S) : Game := 具뵗Game.mk _ _
        (fun x  ((equivShrink g).symm x).1.1.out) (fun x  ((equivShrink g).symm x).1.1.out)具븊r
      suffices {x | x.birthday = a} 굱 Set.image2 f Set.univ Set.univ from small_subset this
      rintro x rfl
      obtain 具빷, rfl, hy'具 := birthday_eq_pGameBirthday x
      let g : Set S := {z | 갞 i, 具뵻.moveLeft i具 = z.1}
      let g : Set S := {z | 갞 i, 具뵻.moveRight i具 = z.1}
      refine 具빦, by simp, g, by simp, ?_具뼆r
      apply PGame.game_eq <| PGame.Equiv.of_exists _ _ _ _ <;>
      intro i
      췅 obtain 具빩, hj具 := ((equivShrink g).symm i).2
        exact 具빩, by simp [PGame.equiv_iff_game_eq, hj]具뼆r
      췅 obtain 具빩, hj具 := ((equivShrink g).symm i).2
        exact 具빩, by simp [PGame.equiv_iff_game_eq, hj]具뼆r
      췅 refine 具빤quivShrink g 具뻑릳具뵻.moveLeft i具, ?_具, i, rfl具, by simp [Quotient.mk_out]具뼆r
        suffices 갞 b 곣 y.birthday, birthday 具뵻.moveLeft i具 < b by simpa [S, hy'] using this
        refine 具_, le_rfl, ?_具뼆r
        exact (birthday_quot_le_pGameBirthday _).trans_lt (PGame.birthday_moveLeft_lt i)
      췅 refine 具빤quivShrink g 具뻑릳具뵻.moveRight i具, ?_具, i, rfl具, by simp [Quotient.mk_out]具뼆r
        suffices 갞 b 곣 y.birthday, birthday 具뵻.moveRight i具 < b by simpa [S, hy'] using this
        refine 具_, le_rfl, ?_具뼆r
        exact (birthday_quot_le_pGameBirthday _).trans_lt (PGame.birthday_moveRight_lt i)
  췅 convert H
    change birthday _ < o  갞 a, _
    simpa using lt_limit ho
```
